{"tid":84112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本身想問鬼妹拎電話","createTime":"2017-01-17T09:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T11:12:39.000Z","uid":13802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"600101136e5c2fa3194b4ed86d07801c47cdccab","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"話說岩先係九龍塘坐地鐵反歸，等車個時撞到個鬼妹，應該都同我差唔多都係20歲左右，矮我小小，佢唔算好靚，不過幾有氣質，咁我眼望佢眼，係車到有時佢都有望下我，我其實好想問佢拎電話，又唔夠膽，所以就拎份notes岀來，寫hi!I want to get ur number,but I am to shy to say it.寫到ur 有位，佢就坐低左，我就縮左沙，本身佢站係我隔離。去到荃灣個邊，我都無拎到電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8e62f97a51fbd6b5613be8318e0c9cd8bf32ee","tid":84112,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:54:30.000Z","msg":"好心你就大方啲聊佢講嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0840eb183de58eb9c32be0b78d3e42262dd9e0fb","tid":84112,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"其實要點先識到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963c6d1e87c922172f4e01150bcf3970217727cc","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"無圖啊 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/17/175454_0dc82e359e0e7b3a2bbd82337d10451b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F175454_0dc82e359e0e7b3a2bbd82337d10451b.jpg&h=def5fe71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbfc14808bd06446778605ff9512151e6810c931","tid":84112,"uid":22382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無圖啊 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/17/175454_0dc82e359e0e7b3a2bbd82337d10451b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F