:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多數鬼妹都唔介意<br />\n<br />\n好鬼nice<br />\n<br />\nbtw 機會過左就冇下冷喇</blockquote><br />\n其實第一次咁想問人拎電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ac4e790b123ddc8065f1e27ace98ad59f806b9","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心你就大方啲聊佢講嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想，唉"},{"pid":"e69d479264de12752f4c958041191acfb43fead5","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"好撚細膽，有無人同我一樣，但又成功踏岀第一步嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba401a4b1e7e8bd4810742fcca12a561bd4f4c4","tid":84112,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩都唔講第一句就攞電話係一定成功嘅"},{"pid":"645d968fa640a043c0833579646ac435b7110109","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩都唔講第一句就攞電話係一定成功嘅</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔係想第一句就拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我又唔知講咩"},{"pid":"dc28fdf48c3ff26de967d9d1a056caa43b82dd9f","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/17/181103_c597bb846144f2ca66d21fad8b53c9bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F181103_c597bb846144f2ca66d21fad8b53c9bf.jpg&h=bbb36d3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be51ee945e8b4b002eba85796d7bc7e73ed6798f","tid":84112,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩都唔講第一句就攞電話係一定成功嘅</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔係想第一句就拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我又唔知講咩</blockquote><br />\n識得個鬼妹佢話有一日響油麻地定唔知邊行行下 有個香港人 審犯咁問佢嘢 仲跟住佢想攞佢電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好做咁嘅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a1d9de3616aae808f6b0718e11ca2dfa7fd9a6","tid":84112,"uid":32833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:39:38.000Z","msg":"撚有望你咩"},{"pid":"e5ed4c76fbb98d4955634a0b24afc01b642bedbd","tid":84112,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"好彩你無埋去炸<br />\n唔係告鳩你騷擾呀仆街"},{"pid":"9b95746a9a09d7f553b67ab3c3486a702498f760","tid":84112,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"證明你唔岩同鬼妹發展<br />\n連講都唔敢講。送到埋口都唔會得米<br />\n所以樓主唔使介懷"},{"pid":"bba88a633e96d8ca49fec02525f04c3c015cd95f","tid":84112,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"佢係我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d9fafe098db9bd9ce3cb93537a04d99aef7acb","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明你唔岩同鬼妹發展<br />\n連講都唔敢講。送到埋口都唔會得米<br />\n所以樓主唔使介懷</blockquote><br />\n成程車，我都唔係好敢望佢，因為佢望過來。其實我都唔係好介懷，不過想下次真係鼓起勇氣問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713ef100cac8728edca40f477ab32621458c5ed0","tid":84112,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:55:38.000Z","msg":"如果再撞番就唔好白費機會啦"},{"pid":"ca64e5303b05252f4938d635172631a5a362ea39","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩都唔講第一句就攞電話係一定成功嘅</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔係想第一句就拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我又唔知講咩</blockquote><br />\n識得個鬼妹佢話有一日響油麻地定唔知邊行行下 有個香港人 審犯咁問佢嘢 仲跟住佢想攞佢電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好做咁嘅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我肯定唔會，我都係想介紹下自己，問下佢咩名，讚佢cute之類，不過算啦，應該做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2b326a80faf37d65cd5140dec790c4618aebc4","tid":84112,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>證明你唔岩同鬼妹發展<br />\n連講都唔敢講。送到埋口都唔會得米<br />\n所以樓主唔使介懷</blockquote><br />\n成程車，我都唔係好敢望佢，因為佢望過來。其實我都唔係好介懷，不過想下次真係鼓起勇氣問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁嘅心態 你下多100次都唔會問到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2e1df032d54af1a0262034778c4fe8d665b094","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩你無埋去炸<br />\n唔係告鳩你騷擾呀仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/17/185651_80c0c12e63414c59e2395693bf9a2f6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F185651_80c0c12e63414c59e2395693bf9a2f6a.jpg&h=c90fbf96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bda87fd8c0bed00f29ad7c92d12cceaab0007e6","tid":84112,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>證明你唔岩同鬼妹發展<br />\n連講都唔敢講。送到埋口都唔會得米<br />\n所以樓主唔使介懷</blockquote><br />\n成程車，我都唔係好敢望佢，因為佢望過來。其實我都唔係好介懷，不過想下次真係鼓起勇氣問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁嘅心態 你下多100次都唔會問到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji